# NETWORK::NETWORK_GET_PRIMARY_CLAN_DATA_PENDING

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns TRUE if data retrieval with NETWORK_GET_PRIMARY_CLAN_DATA_START is pending.
